alone in the dark ii is a 2008 german-american horror film starring rick yune , rachel specter and lance henriksen . the film was directed by peter scheerer and michael roesch . it is a sequel to uwe boll 's 2005 film alone in the dark , although it features an entirely new cast and a story that is unrelated to the original film . alone in the dark ii was filmed in new york city and los angeles . it is loosely based on the infogrames ' alone in the dark video game series .